You can also join our community of digital collectors and cryptocurrency enthusiasts on our discord server (https://discord.gg/sVcVs9KDdS).

ownedNfts.title: ZENITH OF SERENITY
ownedNfts.description: The megalith, known as the Zenith of Serenity, was once a symbol of peacetime for a lost civilisation that existed centuries ago. They had developed a rudimentary form of metalworking, but their society was plagued by wars and conflict. In an effort to end the bloodshed, a group of wise elders came together to create the Zenith of Serenity. Using the knowledge they had gained from the stars and the elements, they forged the megalith and imbued it with a powerful energy that could pacify even the most aggressive warriors. It worked, and for a time, the civilisation was at peace. But as the years passed, the society became complacent, and they began to forget the purpose of the Zenith. They no longer maintained the megalith, and it fell into disrepair. Eventually, it was swallowed up by the lake, and its memory faded into legend. Today, the Zenith of Serenity remains a mysterious and beautiful relic, a testament to the ingenuity and wisdom of the ancient civilisation that created it.
